{"tid":1897014,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"據報今晚北角佛堂再多一人初步確診 為負責清潔的義工","createTime":"2020-02-25T13:03:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T13:28:36.000Z","uid":212626,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"798e1b65cd25aca53f6419e8ff3a6178ce7fe1de","tid":1897014,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T13:03:27.000Z","msg":"可致命的武漢肺炎疫情在本港未受控，今日（25日）新增3宗確診，令香港確診個案增至84宗，2宗涉及北角「福慧精舍」佛堂群組；消息指佛堂一名負責清潔的義工亦初步確診，正在東區醫院留醫。據悉，義工患者前日的測試結果呈陰性反應，今日測試結果呈陽性反應，有可能是採樣問題，也可能是首次採樣測試時病人病毒量未夠高，故今日測試結果才呈陽性反應。至今最少8名曾到過福慧精舍的人受感染，有兩名密切接觸者亦受感染。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200225/JMCQH63N6VRBRHQZ24GXEII5P4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200225%2FJMCQH63N6VRBRHQZ24GXEII5P4%2F&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=f44bdb35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200225%2FJMCQH63N6VRBRHQZ24GXEII5P4%2F&h=ad729a28\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200225/JMCQH63N6VRBRHQZ24GXEII5P4/</a>"},{"pid":"b51218370ad57a0af19934242f03dba0a3d2f91c","tid":1897014,"uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T13:04:18.000Z","msg":"義工患者前日的測試結果呈陰性反應，今日測試結果呈陽性反應<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5222b3754e9d70fb86ec1c345ad2fdd7b66888","tid":1897014,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T13:05:22.000Z","msg":"唔封關 無一倖免<br />\n<br />\n831打死人啊 記唔記我啊 半週年啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1897003\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1897003</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"250818f3594ddcbb413e00cbac73e15d44ce58c4","tid":1897014,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T13:06:34.000Z","msg":"2月8號之後去過佛堂嗰啲都應該要強制驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d3ad94ea1acc9292a439157dbaa930d6eeb